item.title: 【Singles (lossless)】Fred again.. & Obongjayar - adore u [Qobuz Hi-Res 24-bit / 44.1 kHz]
item.description:
Genre: Electronic, Dance
Style: House, Soulful House
Year: 2023
Source: Qobuz

"adore u" is a song by English producer Fred again.. (also known as FRED) featuring the London-based Nigerian singer Obongjayar, released on 11-08-2023 by Atlantic Records. The song is dedicated to the producer’s sister and samples heartfelt lyrics from Obongjayar’s 2022 debut album, Some Nights I Dream of Doors, and a sample from "Stick 'Em" by Fat Boys (1984).
